      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just feel like i've hit a wall and i don't think i can climb over it anymore. the lab results came back again and it's just... everything is falling apart. the funding, the dissertation, even just waking up feels like a chore i didn't sign up for. i've spent my whole life sprinting toward this one goal and now that it's slipping away, i don't even know who i am without it. i'm just so incredibly tired of trying to fight for a life that feels like it's constantly punishing me.",
